179
00:16:58,700 --> 00:16:59,700
Sí.

180
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:03,500
¿Ya has comido?

181
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,000
Aún no.

182
00:17:07,530 --> 00:17:08,530
Hay arroz frito.

183
00:17:17,430 --> 00:17:18,599
